</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 22, NULL, NULL, 590, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Are the assets that directly support the critical service inventoried (technology includes hardware, software, and external information systems)?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
