</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 14, 22, NULL, NULL, 593, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Do specific requirements (such as access permissions or role authorizations) determine which staff members are privileged to modify information assets?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
