<ul>
<li>Standards and guidelines ensure enterprise-wide consistency of service continuity plans.</li>
<li>Standards, guidelines, and templates can be derived by the organization from both internal and external sources.</li>
</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 48, 22, NULL, NULL, 602, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Are service continuity plans developed using established standards, guidelines, and templates?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
