<ul>
<li>Typically this would be done periodically (as defined by the organization).</li>
<li>This can also be done as conditions warrant. Example conditions:</li>
<li>Change in external entity relationship</li>
<li>Change in the critical service operating environment that may affect the resilience requirements.</li>
</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 63, 22, NULL, NULL, 605, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Are these requirements reviewed and updated for each external dependency (i.e.- suppliers, infrastructure providers, and governmental services)?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
