<li>Training needs are established by analyzing the identified skill gaps and identifying the training needed to close those gaps.</li>
</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 68, 22, NULL, NULL, 606, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Have training needs been identified and actioned appropriately?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
