<ul>
<li>Awareness activities must meet the broad needs of staff members.</li>
<li>The activities must be scheduled, advertised (if necessary), resourced, and tracked.</li>
</ul>

To determine if cyber security training activities for the critical service are conducted.
<ul>
<li>The organization must perform cyber security training to ensure that staff is appropriately skilled in their roles.</li>
<li>Training should be planned and scheduled.</li>
<li>Training provided should address identified skill gaps including: (1) training in the use of specialized tools and (2) training in procedures that are new to the individuals who will perform them.</li>
</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 69, 22, NULL, NULL, 606, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Are cyber security awareness activities conducted for the critical service?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
