<ul>
<li>Properly disposing of information assets is necessary to ensure that there are no unauthorized disclosures.</li>
<li>Guidelines for the disposal of information assets should consider: (1) confidentiality requirements, (2) sensitivity categorization, (3) applicable rules, laws, and regulations</li>
</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 16, 23, NULL, NULL, 712, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Do guidelines exist for properly disposing of information assets?', N'Criteria for “Yes” Response
