</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 21, 23, NULL, NULL, 716, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Have cybersecurity human resource practices been implemented for the critical service (e.g., de-provisioning, personnel screening)?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
