<ul>
<li>Some controls have been analyzed against control objectives.</li>
</ul>
')
INSERT INTO [dbo].[MATURITY_QUESTIONS] ([Mat_Question_Id], [Question_Title], [Question_Text], [Supplemental_Info], [Category], [Sub_Category], [Maturity_Level_Id], [Sequence], [Maturity_Model_Id], [Parent_Question_Id], [Ranking], [Grouping_Id], [Examination_Approach], [Short_Name], [Mat_Question_Type], [Parent_Option_Id], [Supplemental_Fact], [Scope], [Recommend_Action], [Risk_Addressed], [Services], [Outcome], [Security_Practice], [Implementation_Guides]) VALUES (813, N'CRE.OP.24', N'', N'<div class="sub-header-1">Question Intent</div><div>To determine if users who attempt to install or connect rogue or unauthorized hardware to the organization’s networks are counseled against adding rogue devices to the organization’s networks.

Ensure a policy addressing the addition of unauthorized hardware to the organization’s networks is developed. The policy should, at a minimum, indicate that adding unauthorized hardware to the organization’s networks is prohibited.

The policy should also direct that awareness training be developed to train users of the issues surrounding the addition of unauthorized or rogue hardware to the organizations networks.
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 23, 23, NULL, NULL, 718, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Are users who attempt to install rogue hardware counseled against installing rogue hardware?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
<ul>
<li>The organization counsels all users who attempt to install rogue or unauthorized hardware to the organization’s networks.</li>
</ul>
')
