<ul>
<li>The organization should evaluate the impact of asset changes on existing resilience requirements.</li>
<li>The requirements from all the services supported by the changed asset should be considered. Evaluating resilience requirements is especially critical when assets are shared between services.</li>
</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 25, 23, NULL, NULL, 711, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Are resilience requirements evaluated as a result of changes to assets?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
