<li>A lessons-learned meeting or review should be held after a major incident with all stakeholders.</li>
<li>Lessons-learned data can be incorporated into the organization''s risk management process, ultimately leading to the selection and implementation of additional controls and improvements to the organization''s protection and sustainment strategies.</li>
