<li>The confidentiality, integrity, and availability requirements of the Incident Management Function are used to derive the collective protection and sustainment requirements of associated assets.</li>
<li>Activities that implement protection and sustainment requirements often appear as processes, procedures, policies, controls, and plans.</li>
</ul>
