</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 159, 23, NULL, NULL, 759, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Is there a standard set of tools and/or methods in use to detect unauthorized mobile code in assets?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
