<ul>
<li>A policy is a written communication from the organization''s senior management to employees.</li>
<li>It establishes the organizational expectations for planning and performing the service continuity management process and communicates those expectations to the organization.</li>
</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 66, 24, NULL, NULL, 800, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Is there a documented policy for service continuity?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
