<ul>
<li>Qualified means that staff are appropriately skilled to perform service continuity management activities.</li>
</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 70, 24, NULL, NULL, 801, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Have qualified staff been assigned to perform service continuity activities as planned?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
