<ul>
<li>The intent is to determine risks that prevent the organization from performing service continuity management activities (service continuity management process), not the risks to the organization if the activities are not performed.</li>
</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 72, 24, NULL, NULL, 801, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Are risks related to the performance of planned service continuity activities identified, analyzed, disposed of, monitored, and controlled?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
