</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 82, 24, NULL, NULL, 805, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Is there management oversight of the performance of situational awareness activities?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
