</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 83, 24, NULL, NULL, 805, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Have qualified staff been assigned to perform situational awareness activities as planned?', N'<div class="sub-header-2">Implemented</div>
