<li>Selecting - from the activities used by business units, divisions, or industry peers - the EDM activities that best meet the needs of the enterprise</li>
<li>Ensuring that the enterprise''s business, policy, and activity objectives are appropriately addressed in these standard, defined activities</li>
<li>Documenting the defined activity</li>
<li>Revising the description of the standard, defined activity as necessary</li>
</ul>
</div>', NULL, NULL, 1, 105, 24, NULL, NULL, 811, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N'Has the organization identified, described, and disseminated standard external dependencies management processes that apply across the enterprise?', N'Criteria for "Implemented" Response
